title: Simon Mall Locations, by City 12/12/07
name: Simon Mall Locations, by City 12/12/07
description:
This dataset displays the locations of all of the listed Simon Mall locations found at their web page and store locater at: http://www.simon.com/findamall
The data was geocoded by city in which the mall is located. Included in this dataset is the name of the mall, type of mall, city and state, year built, gross leasable area by square feet, and stores featured. 
This data was accessed on December 12, 2007
